### 1. Check history (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/endpoints/{{endpointId}}/checks?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Check stats — default range (last 24 hours)
GET {{baseUrl}}/endpoints/{{endpointId}}/checks/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Check stats — explicit range
GET {{baseUrl}}/endpoints/{{endpointId}}/checks/stats?from=2026-07-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-07-06T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Alert history (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/endpoints/{{endpointId}}/alerts?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Dashboard summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
